{"id":612272,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2019/06/【立此存照】寻衅滋事罪不可做无罪辩护？/","date":"2019-06-15T02:20:30Z","modified":"2019-06-15T04:48:01Z","title":"【立此存照】寻衅滋事罪不可做无罪辩护？","content":"<div id=\"attachment_612273\" style=\"width: 560px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/06/责令整改通知书.jpg\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-612273\" class=\"wp-image-612273\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/06/责令整改通知书.jpg\" alt=\"责令整改通知书\" width=\"550\" height=\"618\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/06/责令整改通知书.jpg 1080w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/06/责令整改通知书-267x300.jpg 267w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/06/责令整改通知书-768x863.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/06/责令整改通知书-911x1024.jpg 911w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></a><p id=\"caption-attachment-612273\" class=\"wp-caption-text\"><span style=\"color: #808080;\">图片来源：豆瓣</span></p></div>\n<blockquote><p>责令整改通知书</p>\n<p>上海XX律师事务所：<br />\n你所XXX律师在代理XXX涉嫌寻衅滋事罪、强迫交易罪一案、XXX律师在代理XXX涉嫌寻衅滋事罪一案中，为犯罪嫌疑人做无罪辩护，你所没有组织集体研究。现责令你所进行整改，今后你所律师在办理涉黑涉恶案件过程中，做无罪辩护或改变案件定性时，律师事务所要组织集体研究，依法提出案件处理方案和辩护代理意见。</p></blockquote>\n","author":980,"categories":[18271,18270,18269,27949],"tags":[26898,25968,9239,23705,28122]}